<br>
Well, I'm a Thrust spec'd Highlander Mercenary.  I've used Thrust since release, and I'm going to have to be honest.... half my styles I use regularly in RvR are Thrust.  Pierce, Basiliskfang mostly.  I complement that with Dual Shadows, and Flank/Shadow's Rain.  I keep Dragonfang on my &quot;solo&quot; hotbar along with reflection/hypnotic darkness.<br>
<br>
If you want a change to Thrust to suit your Mercenary, you'll have to do alot more convincing.  My stance for the upcoming style review is DW is for Mercs.  Slash/Crush/Thrust should be geared for classes that have no other specs.  That way, Slash/Crush/Thrust will automatically be useful as filler for a Merc.<br>
