<br>
I think the up-n-coming Crush changes (well, in the UK) are probably Mythic's attempt to give Crush 'identity' or meaning when compared to the other base specs. What they've really done is give this base spec a load of really good utility styles (the like of which I seriously hope DW can get <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  !).... perhaps made (pre-style thinkthrough) to benefit the offensive 'no defense at all FFS' albion tank?<br>
<br>
*Or to stop everyone whining about what the savage has got...<br>
<br>
Anyway, I'm actually hoping they open out the base specs a little more by way of versatility. At the moment, Slash &quot;is&quot; for anyone in plate, Thrust &quot;is&quot; for infiltrators and, well, like I said about Crush. Maybe it should originally have been tailored for the hybrid armsman or something, heh. <br>
<br>
My thought on Saracen Thrust mercs - if you knew you weren't gonna get Dragonfang as a viable style, then you should have just picked your race based on what looks/stats you wanted. I too would love Evade2, though I have no decent moves to do after it (Slash Brit), but our Qui is far from amazing and TBH it's a bit of a joke. On the other hand, you should have great parrying, and though your offensive slash-crush stat (str) and lower HP (by about 50) might balance this out, you will still do better thrust damage than any other Albion merc. Just think you traded 10 con for 10 'offensive-defensive' stat. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm11.showPrevMessage?topicID=87.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm11.showNextMessage?topicID=87.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=87.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm11.emailToFriend?topicID=87.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm11.threadControl?topicID=87.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm11.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=87.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of repl